WEBVTT

00:00:00.956 --> 00:00:05.236
Imagine walking five kilometers
to school every day,

00:00:05.276 --> 00:00:06.796
under the scorching sun,

00:00:06.836 --> 00:00:09.316
no trees, no shed in sight,

00:00:09.316 --> 00:00:13.196
writing final exams outside
in the dry, sweltering heat,

00:00:13.236 --> 00:00:16.916
and still being expected
to pass with flying colors.

00:00:16.956 --> 00:00:19.676
And then after school,
or sometimes before,

00:00:19.676 --> 00:00:20.876
or sometimes both,

00:00:20.916 --> 00:00:23.636
trekking four hours
to the nearest water source,

00:00:23.636 --> 00:00:24.996
standing in long queues

00:00:25.036 --> 00:00:27.756
just to get a few drops
from a drying well.

00:00:27.756 --> 00:00:30.796
This is the daily life of myself